- **MY PAGE 멘토 신청현황(ARTAPMM):** 멘토(`themeType` mentor / 로그인 `MNR`)은 신청목록을 **`POST /api/user/artprom/my-applied/mentor/list`** 로 조회한다(`apiUser.ts` **`USER_ARTPROM.MY_APPLIED_MENTOR_LIST`**). 학생·학부모 등은 기존 **`POST /api/user/artprom/my-applied/list`**(`ARTAPPM`). 본문 JSON **`{ sttusCode? }`** — **ARTAPMM** 상태 필터: **01** 임시저장, **02** 신청, **03** 승인, **04** 완료, **11** 반려, **12** 중단, **99** 취소(**ARTAPPM**의 04=반려·05=중단과 **코드 의미가 다름**; 카드 pill 매핑·셀렉트 옵션을 멘토 전용으로 둔다). 카드 제목 링크: **proGb `08`** → **`/userWeb/bizInputGstudyMentor`**, **`09`** → **`/userWeb/bizInputGstudyMentorLighthouse`**; 쿼리 **`from=mypage`**, **`proId`**, **`proGb`**, **`reqId`**, (해당 시) **`reqEsntlId`**, **`reqGbPosition=4`**, **`type=mentor`**.
- **MY PAGE 멘토 신청 상세(08·09):** `from=mypage`이고 **`reqId`**가 있으면 **`GET /api/user/artappm/mentor-application/by-req-id/{reqId}`**(`apiUser.ts` **`USER_ARTAPPM.MENTOR_APPLICATION_BY_REQ_ID`**)로 **`detail`**·**`fileList`**를 받아 **`BizInputGstudyMentor`·`BizInputGstudyMentorLighthouse`** 폼에 반영한다. 첨부 **`fileId`는 string** 유지(§5); 본인 외 **403**. **조회 전용**: 중복 신청 방지를 위해 **`formActions`(초기화·신청) 숨김**·필드 **`readOnly`/`disabled`**, 기등록 첨부는 **`/api/v1/files/view`** 링크로만 연다. **`reqSub`/`joinTime`** 복원은 **`gstudyMentorSubjectTime.ts`**의 **`parseGstudyMentorApplySubjectFromApi`**, **`parseGstudyMentorHopeTimeFromApi`**(공고 `proTarget`·`schoolGb` 로드 후 희망시간 재해석).
- **MY PAGE 신청 카드 — 선정/미선정/예비(`resultGb`):** 신청자 옆 **`[선정]` / `[미선정]` / `[예비]`** 배지는 **`proGb`가 `01`(청소년 자기계발 연수지원)·`04`(1:1 원어민 화상영어)** 인 건에만 표시한다. 그 외 사업은 **`resultGb`가 있어도 배지를 렌더하지 않는다**(다른 사업에 빈 `resultGb`로 `[미선정]`이 붙는 것을 방지). 구현 참고: `MypageSection`의 `PRO_GB_SHOW_RESULT_SELECTION` · `shouldShowResultSelectionBadge`.

**Reference:** `src/widgets/userWeb/BizInputSection/index.tsx`, `src/widgets/userWeb/BizInputGstudySection/index.tsx`, `src/widgets/userWeb/BizInputGstudyMentorSection/index.tsx`, `src/widgets/userWeb/BizInputGstudyMentorLighthouseSection/index.tsx`, `src/widgets/userWeb/gstudyMentorSubjectTime.ts`, `src/widgets/userWeb/MypageSection/index.tsx`.

### 6.5 Application forms — student row UI by login role (SNR vs PNR)

**When this applies:** Any **support-program application form** under `bizInput` (e.g. `BizInputSection`, `BizInputVdSection`, …) or **공부의 명수** (`BizInputGstudySection`) that displays **student identity** (name / linked child) and loads **ARMUSER** detail for the applicant child.

**Objective (single rule to follow):** Keep **one consistent UX contract** across apply flows:

| Logged-in role (`AuthService.getUserSe()`) | Student row control | Data source |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **SNR** (student) | Read-only **text `input`** (e.g. `className="inputField bgGray"`, `readOnly`) | Logged-in user: `UserArmuserService.getDetail(esntlId)` for **self** |
| **PNR** (parent) | **`<select className="selectField">`** (combobox) listing linked children | `GET /api/user/armchil/children` → options; on change load `UserArmuserService.getDetail(selectedChildEsntlId)`; persist **`cEsntlId` = selected child** in save payload |

**MUST:**

1. **Branch on `userSe`, not on URL alone.** Use `SNR` → readonly input; `PNR` → `select`. Do not show a combobox for the student applying for themselves.
2. **SNR:** Pre-fill the student row from **the logged-in member’s** detail. Do not allow editing the name field on the apply form (profile / MY PAGE is the source of truth).
3. **PNR:** Provide a **placeholder option** (e.g. `value=""`, label like “이름을 선택해주세요”). Load the children list from the **standard** endpoint (`API_ENDPOINTS.USER_ARMCHIL.CHILDREN`). On selection change, refresh dependent student fields (contact, school, address, etc.) from **`getDetail(childEsntlId)`**.
4. **MY PAGE edit (`fromMypage` / `reqId`):** When the application is not editable (`formFieldsLocked` / `sttusCode !== "01"`), **disable** the student `select` the same way as other locked fields (match `BizInputSection`: `disabled={fromMypage}` or equivalent plus lock rules).
5. **Validation:** If PNR and no child selected, use **§6.1 AlertModal + focus** on the student `select` (`aria-required="true"`, no HTML5 `required` on JS-validated fields).
6. **Reuse the canonical pattern** in `BizInputSection` (`studentNameReadonly` vs `studentSelect`) when adding or refactoring other apply screens.

**MUST NOT:**

1. Render **only** a readonly student name **input** for **PNR** without a **child picker** when multiple children may exist.
2. Auto-pick the first child **without** exposing a `select`, unless product explicitly requires it **and** the UI still allows changing selection (prefer combobox for clarity).
3. Use a **combobox for SNR** to “choose self” — redundant and confusing; use readonly input.

**Reference implementations:** `src/widgets/userWeb/BizInputSection/index.tsx` (guardian + student sections; `studentSelect` / `studentNameReadonly`), `src/widgets/userWeb/BizInputGstudySection/index.tsx` (`gstudyStudentSelect` vs `gstudyStudentName`).

**Implementation checklist (before merge):**

- [ ] `SNR` → readonly `input`; `PNR` → `select` + `USER_ARMCHIL.CHILDREN`.
- [ ] Change handler reloads student ARMUSER detail for the selected `esntlId`.
- [ ] MY PAGE / read-only state disables `select` consistently.
- [ ] Submit validation covers empty child selection for PNR (AlertModal + focus).

