**Remember:** User web = HTML-to-React conversion with **design and accessibility preserved**. For file/attachment features, **keep fileId as string** and never use `Number(fileId)` so large ids are not corrupted (§5). Original CSS and class names stay; **CSS is loaded per route** (shared layout: `default.css` + `fonts.css` only; each route layout: only the CSS that route needs; `index.css` only on portal-root). **교육 카드 배지**는 §4.5 — 기본 24×24 통일·커뮤니티 스코프·62×26 재도입 금지. Reference htmltoreact and gunsan.
